    "description": "这是一个受到关注的游戏：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/6da072a50da52377885bcfdc82adda7b.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=586 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/818f1d524ea32470ef2f34165540888a.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=580 /></span><br><br>这是一个开发者用了三年构思，用了将近两年时间开发的有趣的休闲游戏。<br>在这个游戏中，玩家是一个创作者，可以在虚拟世界里创建自己想要的浪漫故事，或者复现出曾经发生过的栩栩如生的爱情、亲情、友情。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一、夏娃之海与3D情人的诞生</h2>玩家会来到夏娃之海Sea of Eva's Origin，在蓝色的海洋上，<br>需要首先创建一个虚拟的女孩，<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/906dbd32a88fcac0b488655ee6a04a53.poster.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/906dbd32a88fcac0b488655ee6a04a53.webm?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/906dbd32a88fcac0b488655ee6a04a53.mp4?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>首先创建女孩的脸蛋，这一步很简单，只需要上传一张照片就可以完成：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/9922d1a25059baf436dc29d71c647985.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=336 /></span> <br> <br>而后需要创建女孩的发型，以及头发的颜色：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/213e9367d51f7b3e272473882ae49c44.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=336 /></span> <br> <br>而后为女孩创建、选择一个身体：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/e5b5f734eb90fc607b627bb65f90426a.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=338 /></span> <br><br>然后为女孩选择衣服：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/6f6b2b134167eb7ebdb4ff0effc9963e.poster.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/6f6b2b134167eb7ebdb4ff0effc9963e.webm?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/6f6b2b134167eb7ebdb4ff0effc9963e.mp4?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br> <br>玩家可以通过完成任务解锁越来越多的衣服。<br>让这个女孩打扮得更加漂亮。<br>我们拥有大量的3D资源来为用户提供不同的服装。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >二、情人之人造灵魂与AI陪聊系统</h2>当然，在我们看来，仅仅是身体可不够算是完美的元宇宙女友。<br>这个游戏有趣的地方在于，创造出的女孩还能够具有自己的性格与星座，<br>并基于创建的性格、对玩家的好感度，与玩家对话、动作互动。<br><br>玩家通过选择设定，赋予确定这个虚拟女孩以一个独有的名字、生日、性格和说话、行为习惯：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/464665454dddcbdd327ccd6c6f30daef.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=336 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/e53cc6c28762e23bb46b9e7f904bc10f.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br> <br>好了现在和这个女孩互动试试吧：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/fd30fc1de934d5532328c37b57bc90c1.poster.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/fd30fc1de934d5532328c37b57bc90c1.webm?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/fd30fc1de934d5532328c37b57bc90c1.mp4?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br> <br>而且，随着与女孩的互动加强，女孩的好感度系统也会产生影响。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >三、约会、虚拟生活</h2>玩家可以在游戏中创建虚拟的家。而且与其它游戏不同，这里的家都是<br>这是一个虚拟的家：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/73893c295f73784db4ad11451af6ce65.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=336 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/e845a300a7a2fb3de83a36213c471d2c.poster.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/e845a300a7a2fb3de83a36213c471d2c.webm?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/e845a300a7a2fb3de83a36213c471d2c.mp4?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>在虚拟的家中，游戏会安排不同的趣味任务.<br>完成任务，可以获得加深好感度的效果，并能 解锁更多的内容<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >四、本游戏还提供了全新的录制系统：</h2><br>录制系统能让玩家像导演那样，计划、排演并录制下所有快乐的幻想<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/0bd3734200d629a87241234e07933f18.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/932c15c683a7946888be8958e5f40b13.poster.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/932c15c683a7946888be8958e5f40b13.webm?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/932c15c683a7946888be8958e5f40b13.mp4?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >五、演唱会玩法：</h2><br>本游戏为用户提供了有趣的音乐游戏玩法。<br><br>演唱会玩法中，我们有大量的节奏性强且流行的音乐来支撑这套系统。<br><br>用户可以通过寻找节拍时机，并敲击按键来演奏不同的音乐。<br><br>在不同的音乐中，角色也可以为您演绎不同的舞蹈。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/1533724bc360231c2936446c0fc4d829.poster.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/1533724bc360231c2936446c0fc4d829.webm?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/1533724bc360231c2936446c0fc4d829.mp4?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/9016e772770ce47b9a0f1b6ad48707da.poster.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/9016e772770ce47b9a0f1b6ad48707da.webm?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/9016e772770ce47b9a0f1b6ad48707da.mp4?t=1703201451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >六、动态壁纸模式，常伴您的桌面</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/967d1442a236fefecfedda3a9594cee0.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><br>这是本游戏的操作按键指南；<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842220/extras/cd4d59d0f84bab1c87f4f8df2c566870.avif?t=1703201451\" width=600 height=336 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >写在最后：</h2>在科幻小说《往日之光》中，作者鲍勃.肖,幻想了一种慢透光玻璃，讲述了一段美丽动人的故事．<br>“想象有一种玻璃，光在这种玻璃中运动的速度极慢，通过半厘米厚需要10年，比蜗牛的速度还慢得多．当一块慢透光玻璃制出来时，望上去总是一片漆黑，因为还没有光穿过它．把这种玻璃放在风景秀丽的林中、湖边，带着这些美丽的景致的光陷入慢透光玻璃中，10年也出不来．把在这种地方放了10年的玻璃镶在城市住宅的窗户上，那么，在下一个10年的过程中，这个窗子外面便仿佛呈现出昔日的美景．空中百鸟飞翔，日夜在交替，季节在变化．一个女子，她的穿着耀艳夺目，她在窗口站了几秒钟，然后回到房中。”<br><br>谨以此游戏，送给我亡故的前女友Jessica。我对她的爱情是那么的深刻，感觉生活中的一切都还存留着她的影子。我非常想念她，因此这几年一直在思索如何开发这样的一款程序。<br><br>佳人犹在，仿佛还盛开在昨天。。。唯有落下的雨滴，仿佛在诉说着凋谢的真实：<br><br>也希望这个游戏，就如一面慢透光玻璃，能安慰世上善男子的心灵。",
